                            span.tooltip__popup
                                a.link.link--blue(href="http://help.inobitec.com/kb/faq.php?id=52" target="_blank") Как узнать?
                    input(type="text" name="issue-code" id="issue-code" data-pattern="[0-9]{4}\\-[0-9]{4}\\-[0-9]{4}\\-[0-9]{4}" data-msg="Поле заполнено не верно" placeholder="0000-0000-0000-0000" inputmode="numeric" required)

